{p} {p}

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE: Free Update patch for Opus Magellan 5.8.
{p} {p}
GPSoftware is proud to demonstrate its continuing support for the
Amiga with the release of a FREE UPDATE patch to its popular File
Management and Workbench Replacement software, Directory Opus
Magellan II.
{p} {p} 
The update is available free to registered users and upgrades Opus
Magellan 5.8 to 5.81. While some new features have been added such
as support for the NewMouse standard, improved OpusFTP operations,
and improved ease of use, this release is mainly a service update
providing solutions to a number of issues identified by end users.
{p} {p}
It is available direct from the GPSoftware web site at
{p} {p}
{link http://www.gpsoft.com.au}http://www.gpsoft.com.au{end}